## Features Implemented

### 1. Product Onboarding
- **18 allopathic** products (cleansers, serums, sunscreens, etc.)
- **15 homeopathic** products (aloe vera, neem, turmeric, etc.)
- Custom product input with type/category selection
- Multi-select with visual selection state

### 2. AI Plan Generation
- Sends selected products + user health profile to **Gemini 2.0 Flash**
- Returns structured morning & night routines with step-by-step instructions
- Includes duration per step and "follow for X days/months" recommendation
- Personalized tips based on skin type

### 3. Daily Routine View
- Morning ☀️ / Night 🌙 routine cards with checkboxes
- Real-time progress bar showing steps completion
- Day navigation (← →) to view/edit previous days
- "Update Products" button to re-generate plan

### 4. Calendar & History
- Monthly calendar grid with day-level completion status (✅ 🟡 —)
- Click any past day to view and **retroactively edit** its tasks
- Month navigation
- Changes persist immediately via API

---

## API Endpoints

| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| GET | `/api/skincare/plan` | Get current products + plan |
| POST | `/api/skincare/plan` | Save products → generate AI plan |
| POST | `/api/skincare/log` | Log/update daily task completion |
| GET | `/api/skincare/log/:date` | Get log for a specific date |
| GET | `/api/skincare/calendar` | Get last 31 days of logs |

